<p class="">Whether or not it is desirable to publish the Report of the judicial inquiry, would my right hon. Friend explain how it can be right to withhold the result of that inquiry from a man who was the principal witness and who is principally affected by it? How can it be right to withhold the Report from Seretse himself?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
